noticeDescription: Take notice that the Council of the City of Toronto has passed By-law 370-2021 to designate 938 (including entrance addresses at 940 and 942 King Street West), 944, and 950 King Street West and 95, 97, and 99 Strachan Avenue (Spadina-Fort York, Ward 10) as being of cultural heritage value or interest.
